# Email Sending Service

## Overview

This project implements a resilient email sending service using JavaScript. It supports retry logic with exponential backoff, fallback between providers, idempotency, rate limiting, and basic status tracking.

## Features

- Retry mechanism with exponential backoff
- Fallback between two mock email providers
- Idempotency to prevent duplicate emails
- Basic rate limiting
- Status tracking
- (Bonus) Circuit breaker pattern
- (Bonus) Simple logging
- (Bonus) Basic queue system

## Setup

1. **Install Dependencies**
   ```bash
   npm install
   ```
   2.To Run these
   '''bash
   npm test
